A handy form panel to create a CSS text style.

!! ATTENTION !!
This extension requires the Ext.ux.ColorPicker extension which you can find here : https://github.com/osnoek/Ext.ux.ColorPicker


Simply drop the files into the root of an ExtJs 4.x install folder.

An example page can be found in: INSTALL_DIR/examples/stylepicker.html

usage : 
To create the stylepicker panel:
var stylepicker = Ext.widget('ux.stylepicker', {
	renderTo : Ext.getBody(),
		styleConfig : {
		'font-size' : '20px'	
	}
});

To create a stylepickerfield : 
var stylepicker = Ext.widget('ux.stylepickerfield', {
	renderTo : Ext.getBody(),
	styleConfig : {
		'font-size' : '20px'	
	}
});
